---
layout: layouts/base.njk
section: contact
---
<header class="contact-hero">
  <h1>say hi.</h1>
  <p class="sub">I try to answer everything (all legit looking messages at least). It might take me <b>a few days</b> if I'm heads-down on something, but it will get a reply.</p>
</header>

<section class="contact-grid">
  <div>
    <div class="contact-card">
      <div class="meta" style="margin-bottom:10px">email · preferred</div>
      <div class="email">
        <a class="addr" href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.emailLabel }}</a>
        <button type="button" class="cp" id="copyEmail" data-email="{{ site.email }}">↘ copy</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="socials">
      <a href="{{ site.links.github }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="n">github</span> <span class="arr">↗</span></a>
      <a href="{{ site.links.twitter }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="n">x / twitter</span> <span class="arr">↗</span></a>
      <a href="{{ site.links.linkedin }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="n">linkedin</span> <span class="arr">↗</span></a>
      <a href="{{ site.links.instagram }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="n">instagram</span> <span class="arr">↗</span></a>
    </div>

    <div class="postit">
      <b>note:</b> I'll always make time to chat about founding eng, weird hardware, or anything you're tinkering on.
    </div>
  </div>

  {% include "components/form.njk" %}
</section>

{% if layoutContent %}
<section class="body prose" style="padding-top: 0;">
  {{ layoutContent | safe }}
</section>
{% endif %}
